commit.message:
configure: Regenerate using autoconf 2.59.

2007-04-25  Janne Blomqvist  <jb@gcc.gnu.org>

	* configure: Regenerate using autoconf 2.59.
	* Makefile.in: Likewise.  
	* config.h.in: Likewise.

From-SVN: r124142
